node.text:
In order to stretch our capacities and grow as humans, we are required to do things we haven’t yet done.

Imposter syndrome is something we all feel when we’re pushing these boundaries and treading into not-yet-known territory. Everyone feels this same thing. When you realize this, you won’t have any reason left to stop yourself. 

#impostersyndrome #personalgrowth #trusttheprocess

🎥 by @maxwmccoy
🎶 "Remember Jah" by the incredible @satsang

node.title: How To Push Past Self-Imposed Boundaries

node.text:
I wake up with an anxiousness in my chest. Am I doing enough? Am I serving the world in the best way that I can?

Sometimes I fall into hopelessness. A depression rolls in like a fog. “I’ll never be able to do enough. People will continue to cheer the violations of our divinity and hurl abuses at their neighbors, as long as they can feel like they are better than someone else.” 

But I know, I know, I know that I am not alone. And I’ve never felt that more deeply than after this past week @soltarahealingcenter. The whole cosmos of allies seen and unseen are conspiring to help us.

Ayahuasca, the great mother, is reaching with her vine to heal the hearts and minds of her people.

A real life Dragon, Maestro Orlando, is singing his magic into the world.

My Queen @vylanamarcus and my sisters and brothers like @mehcadbrooks are with me to the end.

My @fit.for.service tribe is strong and full of heart, as are so many of you.

This is the fight we have known was coming. And we’re here for it. Hoka!

For more on my experience with Maestro Orlando check out my latest podcast with @duncantrussell and to reach out to “El Dragon” head to MaestroOrlando.com 🐉

📸 @maxwmccoy

Photo by Aubrey Marcus in Austin, Texas. May be an image of text that says 'Aubrey Marcus @AubreyMarcus We want things. But we don't want to pay the price. In fact we always want the things that we aren't willing to pay the price to attain. We want to just want, not get. Because the price isn't money. The things we really want require genuine sacrifice.'.

node.text:
We want great health, but are we willing to eat clean, train hard, and sleep long?

We want to make a difference, but are we willing to sacrifice partying, leisure, and our favorite distractions to do it?

We want unconditional love.  But are we willing to give unconditional love, to ourselves and others?

Everything has a price. It’s just a matter of what we are willing to pay ❤️

#sacrifice #goals #goforyourwin

Love you no matter what, just as you are, and you are always forgiven. expect nothing and am grateful for everything. give you the truth only and always. You are learning in the perfect way." Give this gift to yourself first'.

node.text:
There are a lot of ways we try to show Love. There are even books written about “love languages”. But Love in its raw and wild form needs no translation. It just is. 

Give Love and you give the gift of a king or queen, at the price any pauper can pay.

#love #lovequotes #selflove

node.text:
The lighter you travel, the more enjoyable the journey. And nothing is more effervescent than the present moment. 🤍

#bepresent #letgoofthepast #presence

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Aubrey Marcus in Costa Rica. May be an image of 1 person and text that says '"WHEN WE ARE NO LONGER ABLE TO CHANGE A SITUATION- WE ARE CHALLENGED TO CHANGE DURSELVES." -VIKTOR E. FRANKL'.

node.text:
There is no better example of a situation we cannot change, than one that happened in the past. But nonetheless we will ruminate on whatever it is, as if we had a time machine in our pocket. Nothing in the past can change. But your response to everything that happened in the past is up to you. Will you allow it to make you stronger? Will you forgive yourself? Can you be grateful, no matter how hard it was? It’s all a choice. And making that choice is how you change yourself, right now in the present moment.

Artist: Anatheme 

#changequotes #acceptance #changeyourlife
